Simple GLFW test suite

Actually, more like debugging tools for the devs.

Descriptions
============

tearing
-------

Visual test to see whether vsync (swap interval) works.

events
------

Simple event dumper, run from console/terminal to see events.

reopen
------

Simple stress test for window closing and re-opening.

fsaa
----

Visual test to see whether FSAA works.

peter
-----

Very specific mouse event test for examining a series of bugs reported by peterpp.

accuracy
--------

Visual test for mouse cursor position accuracy.

